					<description><![CDATA[I had a great time at Clockwork Alchemy!  I was delighted to watch my Twist go out into the world, in good hands.  Not to mention, of the massive stack of books I brought with me, I sold out!!  *faints* As promised, here are photos of some of the lovely people who bought a copy [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I had a great time at Clockwork Alchemy!  I was delighted to watch my Twist go out into the world, in good hands.  Not to mention, of the massive stack of books I brought with me, I sold out!!  *faints*</p>
<p>As promised, here are photos of some of the lovely people who bought a copy at the con.  I&#8217;m sorry to say that I didn&#8217;t get everyone by pure, scatterbrained forgetfulness.  So, if you bought a copy and don&#8217;t see your photo here, please don&#8217;t take offense.   I would have taken a shot if I&#8217;d remembered.  Everyone&#8217;s costumes were so lovely!  I just have to show off.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="04KjOk on Make A Gif, Animated Gifs" src="http://makeagif.com/media/5-31-2013/04KjOk.gif" width="450" height="337" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Did you spot me?  Here&#8217;s a shot of my (super easy thanks to Halloween) costume, and my synth dread fohawk, in the authors&#8217; library.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="me" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/me.jpg" width="450" height="337" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Me and my super cute dragon!</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-448 alignnone" style="margin-right:5px;" alt="dragon 2" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon-2.jpg?w=300" width="270" height="203" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon-2.jpg 1280w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon-2-300x225.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 270px) 100vw, 270px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-449 alignnone" style="margin-left:5px;" alt="dragon1" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon1.jpg?w=300" width="270" height="203" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon1.jpg 1280w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon1-300x225.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/dragon1-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 270px) 100vw, 270px" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Mom and I, braving a dark and mysterious London backstreet&#8230;</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone  wp-image-451" alt="mom" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/mom.jpg?w=1024" width="553" height="415" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/mom.jpg 1280w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/mom-300x225.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/mom-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px" /></p>
<p>Good times &#8230; good times&#8230;  Well, thanks again to everyone to came to visit us at the con!  I was really a blast, I learned a lot, and I can&#8217;t wait for next year.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
